{"tid":2223240,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[曼聯]咩咩妹請入","createTime":"2020-09-29T16:01:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T08:45:07.000Z","uid":96525,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b0523bba455e7548f548523d5e9e0b17d0b19b29","tid":2223240,"uid":96525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:01:37.000Z","msg":"不經不覺你已經從地球畢業兩年了<br />\n每年中秋對你倍感思念<br />\n除了跟你離開的日子很接近<br />\n你還在的時候總愛老屈我拿很多大班冰皮月餅到上水火車站散貨<br />\n你肯定猜不到現在上水沒有一車車的支那人吧<br />\n<br />\n如果你還未投胎的話請去害死木狗吧<br />\n曼聯仍然很垃圾但不關福仔事<br />\n要關都關普巴事吧<br />\n也不要放過害過你的ryo狗賤男人<br />\n還有跟你挽過text sex的爵士連加特<br />\n騙財(2000萬)騙色的賤男人<br />\n我已經揭開牠扮純情的真面目<br />\n希望你也可以懲罰牠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eMLAozO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeMLAozO.png&h=4d8f56fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜我仍未找到方法見返你！我會繼續努力！<br />\n我記得你條仔說元氣大滿足有omakase質素<br />\n現在變了藍店真可惜<br />\n如果你還在的話應該天天論政吧<br />\n謝謝你送我人生中最珍貴的禮物！下年再見！"},{"pid":"9684baba9c0ee878adaec3b8d0396bec7ceefa56","tid":2223240,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:05:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60512b88f5374ba5f4a7ffa96efa11fb236c960b","tid":2223240,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:13:59.000Z","msg":"佢呃左波台手足買匯豐單野點計？"},{"pid":"7ee4893dc1ba935ffb36f25612cd750bfbe1fc70","tid":2223240,"uid":96525,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"60512b88f5374ba5f4a7ffa96efa11fb236c960b","tid":2223240,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:13:59.000Z","msg":"佢呃左波台手足買匯豐單野點計？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:18:07.000Z","msg":"當交智商稅"},{"pid":"9267d238885969aa5b52e95d8fab0569e1face17","tid":2223240,"uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60512b88f5374ba5f4a7ffa96efa11fb236c960b","tid":2223240,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T1